item.title: FIRED UP BY THE THINGS THAT MATTER
item.description: One person’s trash is someone else’s treasure. This was how Elise Aguilar discovered the latent photographer in her. About 2 decades ago, while in college, Elise was introduced to her lifelong passion when a friend decided to upgrade his photo gadgets and give away his manual SLR, complete with fancy lenses and accessories, packed in a really nice bag. This friend’s refuse turned out to be one of the best gifts that Elise ever received in her lifetime.
